    dc:title "Contributions to the millipede fauna of China: five new species of the genus Nepalella Shear, 1979 (Diplopoda, Chordeumatida, Megalotylidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235141>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235143>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235147>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235151> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235141>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39–42. Nepalella labolensis sp. nov., male holotype (ZMUM). 39. Basal part of leg pair 10, caudal view. 40.Anterior gonopods, frontal view (apex of coxite on the left broken off). 41. Posterior gonopods, frontal view. 42. Posterior gonopods, caudal view. Abbreviations: a, angiocoxite; b, bush-like structure; bb, basal blade; bl, anterior colpocoxital blade; cxi, coxite; lp, flattened process; mb, mesal blade; ml, median lobe; mp, mesal process. Scales: 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7235141/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235143>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43–46. Nepalella labolensis sp. nov., male holotype (ZMUM). 43, 44. Anterior gonopods, caudal and frontal views, respectively. 45. Posterior gonopods, caudal view. 46. Posterior gonopods, frontal view. Abbreviations: a, angiocoxite; b, bush-like structure; bb, basal blade; bl, anterior colpocoxital blade; lp, flattened process; mb, mesal blade; mp, mesal process. Scales: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7235143/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235147>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52–55. Nepalella shimianensis sp. nov., male holotype (ZMUM). 52. Posterior gonopod, caudal view. 53. Posterior gonopod, frontal view. 54. Posterior gonopod colpocoxite, caudal view. 55. Distal part of posterior gonopod colpocoxite, caudal view. Abbreviations: a, angiocoxite; bl, anterior colpocoxital blade; bs, boat-shaped structure; lp, lateral process; m, median process; op, ovale part. Scales: 10 μm (Fig. 55), 20 μm (Fig. 54), 100 μm (Figs 52, 53)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7235147/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7235151>
    dc:description "FIGURES 59–65. Nepalella zhumanica sp. nov., male holotype (ZMUM). 59. Leg pair 10, frontal view. 60. Basal part of leg pair 10, frontal view. 61. Basal part of leg pair 11, caudal view. 62. Posterior gonopods, caudal view. 63. Distal part of posterior gonopod colpocoxite, frontal view. 64. Anterior gonopods, caudal view. 65. Posterior gonopods, frontal view. Abbreviations: a, angiocoxite; b, broom-like process; bl, anterior colpocoxital blade; cxi, coxite; d, digitiform process; db, lateral blade; lb, flat plate; mb, mesal branch; ml, median lobe; s, coxal process; tb, thin blade; tp, tongue-like process;. Scales: 20 μm (Figs 60–61, 63–64), 100 μm (Figs 59, 62, 65)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7235151/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

